Yihoowa ashkkarati bantta kahaa loohissanawu koyoosona.
Eti likkebaanne likke gidennabaa, loˈˈobaanne iitabaa xeelliyaagan bantta kahay yootiyoobay Xoossa Qaalay yootiyoobaara maayettanaadan koyoosona.
